high_descs: Pick up the potato from the counter.
Rinse the potato off in the water and pick the potato back up.
Put the potato into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a Potato and place it into a Fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the potato next to the sink.
Turn and go to the edge of the sink to your left.
Put the potato in the sink, turn the water on, then take it out.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a Potato and put it in the Fridge.

high_descs: walk over to the cutting board that is on top of the sink.
pick up the potato from the cutting board.
take it over to the kitchen sink.
Put the potato in the kitchen sink and wash it.
After washing remove and walk to the fridge.
Open the door and put the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Getting the potato from the cutting board and putting it in the fridge.
